A_377 - Every time something new is invented, it is important that there is the work of professionals in certain sectors to fully understand its impacts and any other valid uses that can be made of it. Each object is typically thought of for one use, but in reality it can conceptually have more than one. The important thing is that it is intelligent use. However, improving existing products or inventions or finding new uses for them is also useful, we have a lot that can be improved or possibly recycled or reused in a creative and intelligent way.